      "markdown": "10.引导结果状语从句的从属连词有：so that(结果是)和so/such…that \n\n(如此…以至于)等.\n\nIt was very coldso that the wter in the bol frooe.\n\nIt is such a heavy box that nobody can move it.\n\n11.引导比较状语从句的从属连词有：as…as(与…一样)，not as/so…as…\n\n(不及，赶不上)，和that(比)等.\n\nI know you better than she does.\n\nHe works as carefully as she.\n\nI can't run as/so fast as you.\n\n12.引导名词性从句的从属连词有：that 和 if /whether是否等.\n\nWe know that the earth goes around the sun.(从句\n\nWhether he'll go there hasn't been decided.(主语从句)\n\n[注意]在时间状语从句和条件状语从句中，如果主句是将来时，从句要\n\n用一般现在时。\n\n",
